{"title":"CentOS折腾日记","date":"2019-08-10T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Aug 10, 2019","L":"08/10/2019","MM-DD":"08-10"},"thumbnail":"https://blog-1251959181.file.myqcloud.com/centOS.jpg","link":"2019/08/10/CentOS","comments":true,"tags":["Linux","Note"],"categories":["Coding"],"updated":"2020-03-29T17:40:22.700Z","content":"<p>不会后端的前端不是个好全栈</p>\n<h2 id=\"初始配置\">初始配置<a title=\"#初始配置\" href=\"#初始配置\"></a></h2>\n<p>centOS系统最小安装以后是没有网络连接的，同时也没有安装网络工具，vim等，不能使用<code>ifconfig</code>命令，配置步骤如下：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>ip addr</code>查看网卡名</li>\n<li><code>vi /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-xx</code>修改对应网卡文件<code>ONBOOT=yes</code></li>\n<li><code>service network restart</code>重启网络服务</li>\n<li><code>yum install net-tools</code>安装网络工具，安装成功后即可使用<code>ifconfig</code>命令</li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"ffmpeg命令整理","link":"2019/08/13/ffmpeg"},"next":{"title":"Linux常用命令整理","link":"2019/08/06/Linux_commond"},"plink":"https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/2019/08/10/CentOS/","toc":[{"id":"初始配置","title":"初始配置","index":"1"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Vincente Liang","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/2019/08/10/CentOS/\" title=\"CentOS折腾日记\">https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/2019/08/10/CentOS/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"August 10, 2019","updated":"March 29, 2020"}}